      "date": "2019-01-27 09:16:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nCory, I don't see this as a particularly critical.  It is not something that is hit by users under any kind of normal usage, though I agree the consequences are severe.\n\nI think someone will get to it eventually, but it isn't a priority to get it landed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
